 companies expect every employee to understand how to use spreadsheets to document information and perform calculations. Financial and data analysts use Excel and VBA to build interactive spreadsheet models to perform repetitive analyses. 								I'm learning to use Excel and VBA to build interactive data models. These models can be used to assess investment projects at personal and corporate scales. 							 																	Project Management							I joined the HSBC Group as a Global Operations Graduate Trainee in July 2021. Project management is one of the required skills for success on this post according to veteran operations managers at the global bank. 								As I said, my career goals direct my research activities. Therefore, I'm currently studying project management to learn to manage projects cost effectively. I believe this is an important skill for managerial roles at financial institutions and beyond. 							 			"
