ess. As a web developer, I'm committed to acquiring the skills 		in WordPress theme development. Knowing WordPress will help me build better web applications for clients. 	 			I started this journey at the beginning of February 2022. I've been trying to turn one of my template designs into a 		fully functional WordPress website. I've made good progress on this initiative. Once I master the basics of WordPress 		theme development, I will publish this new website. 	 	Jekyll Theme: 			Jekyll is an excellent static site generator that enables developers to build stunning static websites from 		markdown files. Jekyll uses Ruby and Liquid to create reusable templates, allowing users to focus on the actual		content and build webpages easily. This tool helps minimise errors from manual handling of HTML code. 	 "
