ffice suit software. These software are accepted into global markets, and as more people use them, the better these open-source software projects get. In the next couple of days, I will try out these alternatives. There is a good chance; however, that I will stick to WPS Office because it’s homemade. As a Chinese citizen, I’m proud of supporting the People’s Republic of China through the lens of commerce. If more of us use Made in China, it will get better and become more competitive players on the global stage. "
