ebook, would be limited and reviewed case by case for approval. The Entity List is a tool I developed to identify and manage security risks in both physical and digital worlds. Entities designated following Entity List designation and implementation rules will be subject to a string of sanctions that deprive them access to my data. After being included on the List, I will no longer use Facebook or any Meta Platforms products or services unless there is absolutely no alternative, which won’t be the case considering that Meta has some competitors and this world is so diverse. I’m sharing this unpleasant experience with Facebook on my website with you all to highlight the risks of using Facebook or other Meta Platforms products and services. Please, please, please exercise caution when choosing media platforms. It is highly recommended to: #DeleteFacebook #DeleteInstagram #DeleteWhatsApp #BoycottMetaPlatforms "
